      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MINESITE (3) has been thereabouts without winning, the latest when fourth in a BM70 and not far from the winner. This far easier and gets chance to find some winning form. BEFORE THE WAR (2) is also down in class, tackling the same grade but richer company last time at Pakenham. Looks well placed here and expected to take running down. SURPRISATIC (1) is a great form lately including a last start Swan Hill win. Last time here ran on hard for a course and distance win. Honest and will be winding into the finish. KAMEZALI (5) resumes for a new yard and is fitter for three jump-outs, placing the last two. Has the ability and worth keeping safe. HERE COMES WOZZA (4) has pace and looks a major player on best form.",
